room_title: Escape room "The Asylum" by Source Code Escape Games in Augusta
room_description: The Broad Street Sanitarium has a dark secret. While urban legends and tales of hauntings swirl around the mere mention of its name, the real question is, what atrocities occurred to cast such a damning curse within its hallowed walls? It's up to you to uncover the secrets of the Asylum. Get out, tap out, or fall victim. The choice is yours.
